問，問左兩個月<br />\n唔好話我冷氣軍師 因為有出去 有份講<br />\n<br />\n做乜撚次次封淨條行人路?<br />\n你既目的係乜撚野? 目的係阻止狗行丫嘛 減低佢速度丫嘛<br />\n咁你阻止得黎 扎好鐵馬 三角又好 打平放又好<br />\n但你封漏條行人路喇位 做乜撚?<br />\n<br />\n咁班狗由果個行人路位集體一行，就過左個鐵馬陣啦<br />\n屌你老母真係好撚嬲"},{"pid":"d4ae4604ea78841e5ac4fecdeb7ddb6a51194d8c","tid":1504141,"uid":267801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:43:01.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過加轆進攻用。"},{"pid":"0bbec3f6539c0146487f5c2013bc9d1a6356f861","tid":1504141,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T09:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"657c807642ee8d308f23b49109883c2f4d2be2fe","tid":1504141,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T09:18:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5243d4530db124e8240ea0bd0ec3b163c030263","tid":1504141,"uid":134778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T09:19:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27feadf1b8c5bd2eca11c1399a0a79ac973f3c6c","tid":1504141,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T09:24:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}